snippet.title: Soggy Beans | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Fish will come, fish will go. Take photos, collect beans, decorate your seascape, then relax or do other things while your friends swim by in this calming side-idler 🐡

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2636430/Soggy_Beans/

Stay up to date with RATMODE:
Website: https://ratmode.games/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/wVcsytwD3S

Music by Finn Paul: 
https://www.finnpaulmusic.com/
